# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
The issue is caused by package @angular/common/locales


### Is this a regression?

Yes, the previous version in which this bug was not present was: 9.1.11


### Description

Importing a locale for use with [registerLocaleData](https://angular.io/api/common/registerLocaleData) causes angular 10 to complain:
> CommonJS or AMD dependencies can cause optimization bailouts.
> For more info see: https://angular.io/guide/build#configuring-commonjs-dependencies

